Package: rWDPA
Title: Query the ProtectedPlanet.net WDPA API
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-11-27
Authors@R: person("Luis J.", "Villanueva-Rivera", email = "ljvillanueva@coquipr.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Query the World Database on Protected Areas API from
    ProtectedPlanet.net. You will need to request an API key from https://
    api.protectedplanet.net before using this package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    jsonlite,
    geojsonio
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
BugReports: http://github.com/ljvillanueva/rWDPA/issues
